children.title: Rain drenches Easter campers at
children.description:
Rain drenches Easter campers at Rickmansworth ._x000D_
Campers arriving at Rickmansworth , Hertfordshire , to spen Easter under canvas found that the weather had given their holiday an inauspicious start . They had to erect their tents in heavy rain . _x000D_
Photo shows , erecting a tent in the rain at Rickmansworth ._x000D_

children.title: Lynmouth Floods
children.description:
Lynmouth floods  1952_x000D_
Lynmouth 's homeless move into caravan homes ._x000D_
Homeless victims of the Lynmouth floods are moving into their new caravan home , on a site at Great Holman Park in the beautiful setting of the Valley of the Rocks .  Photo shows:  Soldiers who help to make the new Lynmouth also keep the children happy , playing with Mrs Stirling and family in front of their new caravan home .  _x000D_
30th August 1952

children.title: Kinderbuch
children.description:
Theo macht Ferien
Wiese & Wald & Fluß & Zelt & Caravan & Urlauber : Mann & Frau & Kind & Spielzeug : Puppe & Junge : Theo
OPp.-Einband mit Illustration (Urlauber mit Caravan und Zelt auf einer Wiese mit Fluß, darüber, sitzend im O seines Namens, der Junge Theo); 13 doppelseitige Abbildungen, mit eingedrucktem Text (mit Frontispiz und Innendeckelillustration). Mit Fragen zur Schulung des Wahrnehmungs- und Ausdrucksvermögens.
